data.description: Hard to find rural location located in Patrick Henry schools. This nicely updated home features 3 bedrooms, 1 bath and a 40 x 30 pole barn on .43 acres. Home features updated metal roof (2 yrs), new shop door, updated garage door, vinyl plank floor covering, vinyl windows, updated baseboard heat, updated bath and more. Shop is heated with wood or propane. Large shop door is 11 feet high. Kitchen has new cupboards and counter tops and includes stainless range/oven and refrigerator.
